Simhasan aka &quot;The Throne&quot; 1980 ~ Jabbar Patel Classic Marathi(Indian) Movie

Poster &lt;a href=&quot;
http://desibbrg.org/images/35308290500273807838.jpg&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
